An embodiment of the present invention will now be described with reference to the accompanying figures, wherein:
Figures 1a and 1b illustrates a child safety gate with securing means according to an embodiment of the present invention in a substantially erect position and a substantially folded position (with the barrier material removed) respectively;
Figures 2a-2e illustrate the child safety gate in figures 1a from a front view, plan view from above, end view, folded view with the barrier material removed, and exploded folded view with the barrier material removed respectively;
Figures 3a and 3b show securing means according to an embodiment of the present invention in an extended position and a retracted position respectively;
Figures 4a and 4b show a cross sectional view taken through the securing means in figures 3a and 3b respectively; and
Figure 5 shows an exploded view of the securing means in figures 3a-4b.
